title: MarketWatch: The Post-Moratorium Outlook for Residential Real-Estate I
description: MarketWatch reporter Jacob Passy interviews Daren Blomquist, vice president of market economics at Auction.com, about how the end of the nationwide foreclosure and eviction moratoriums has affected investors' appetite for residential real-estate.
